reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great to have spares on hand!
reviews.reviewText: I like to have one or two screen protector spares on hand in the event that I drop my phone and crack the one I am using. I don’t like having to go without a screen protector (or using a cracked one) while waiting for a replacement to arrive. Overall, these are good screen protectors and easy to install. I do not use the camera protectors.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 24, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Great screen protector but camera lens protector did not work for me
reviews.reviewText: The front screen protector was relatively easy to install using the included cloth. I had no bubbles or other issues after installation.-1 star because the camera lens protector (back of camera) did not work. I cleaned the lens and applied the protector but my camera kept recognizing it as an object and trying to take photos in macro mode. I finally had to remove it completely.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect screen protectors
reviews.reviewText: These are easy to install and do not attract air bubbles. I’ve had some that need to be reset multiple times. This landed perfectly on the first try and has lasted me months. The camera protector did get cracks, enough that I had to remove it because it was effecting how my pictures were taken. I suppose that is its job though, so well done!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 1, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Wonderful Glass and Easy to Apply
reviews.reviewText: I crack screen protectors on my iPhone like its my job! So, I'm always shopping around for good deals on screen glass kits. This one is a real nice kit that includes all the things you need for a perfect application. It has the wet and dry wipe to clean the screen. More importantly, it has the plastic screen guide which ensures you are able to put on the glass in exactly the right location. This is an essential component to a good kit. My glass looks beautiful on my iPhone 14, and I would highly recommend this one.I also decided to use the camera lens protector for the back. It gets the job done well. The one thing I don't like about the camera protection is that the piece is made of plastic. This means that it won't be long before it gets scratched up, and that will begin to interfere with the quality of my photos. Because this camera protector wasn't really the reason I picked up this kit, it doesn't impact my satisfaction. But, do keep this in mind if you care about this part of the kit.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good screen protector with alignment tool!
reviews.reviewText: This is another good screen protector for the Pixel 7a. It includes an alignment tool that you can snap onto the phone to make installation easy. Be sure to clean your screen thoroughly first and install it in a clean location to prevent dust from getting stuck to it and causing bubbles.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Installation was straightforward and didn't seem to take a lot of time/effort.Sadly when it was done there were tiny bubbles under the screen protector, despite being scrupulous about cleaning the screen and avoiding dust. "Interestingly" they seemed to be mostly along the edges. Playing around a bit I did find I could use a fingernail to press them out, but it felt like playing space invaders for an hour or so. I still have a couple of tiny bubbles at the edge that seem to be resisting being pressed out but I don't even notice them unless I go to look for them.I did have to re-do my fingerprint scans, something I might not have known about had I not read another review. There were no directions in the package and I'm not willing to go to a Facebook page to see if there are directions there.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good screen protector for the money
reviews.reviewText: The protector is made of good quality material that is thick enough to thoroughly protect your phone yet still allow for touchscreen actions and bio-metric security. Both the screen protector and camera lens protector are easy to install. Overall, I am very satisfied and would recommend to others.
